Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"20 Years' Worth of Prayers!\NTake Back the Land of Wano"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that fist...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can punch a hole in Onigashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.05,0:02:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move Onigashima out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not do it, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.73,0:02:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, right, Momo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.81,0:02:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Move Onigashima out of your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's settle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That burns!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to grab me!\NI'm not gonna run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know something, Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a hero of this country\Nwas burned to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, this country has been lawless!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are the heroes\Nthat they've been waiting 20 years for!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Dragon Torch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:13.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,FLAME DRAGON TORCH
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to throw that right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're gonna melt away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:04:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...not gonna melt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned from the old man\Nhow to throw a punch without even a touch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You call it Haki,\Nbut we call it Ryuo in the Land of Wano.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't strain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow the unused Haki in your body\Nto flow to your fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna knock you down to the abyss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rising Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bajrang...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Bagua!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening out there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Straw Hat-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.39,0:06:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's Straw Hat-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Straw Hat-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.27,0:06:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, straw hat man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Please!\N--Take him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! To Kuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oden... {\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to guess\Nwhere the samurai are heading!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kozuki Clan's heir is at the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them all! Eradicate the Kozuki Clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exterminate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exterminate them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go finish things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with the Kozuki Clan anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can shoot\Nwhoever stands against the Shogun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Witness how deep\Nthe Kurozumi Clan's grudge is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid Kozuki Clan admirers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Oden's wife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We confirmed her death in Bakura Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one else escaped from Oden Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the Kozuki Clan is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you Daimyo, choose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:56.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,RINGO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether to enliven {\i1}our{\i0} Land of Wano...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:08:58.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,UDON
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or to fight a war!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:00.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,KIBI
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what we'll say...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:06.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,HAKUMAI
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a nonsense question!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kozuki Clan is our only Shogun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Avenge Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect the Land of Wano to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid of the enemies! Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.23,0:09:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast Breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:50.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,RINGO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:51.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,HAKUMAI
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:52.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,UDON
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:53.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,KIBI
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are so weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Samurai's determination"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't live up to\Nyour title as samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn samurai are pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be frustrating for you to lose to me,\Nwho you have looked down on as a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weak can't protect anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fools! Listen carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, this country will be\Ntinged the color of the Kurozumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring all the young men who can work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make weapons nationwide!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Work yourself to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn all the useless trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crops won't grow in this soil...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no drinking water or food...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen to this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody, help! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna live today, work!\NYou vermin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those resources are more important than you!\NIf you handle them roughly, I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scream if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will come help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an isolated country.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather die...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't jump the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:12:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winter's coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A long, long winter...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what Toki-{\i1}sama{\i0} said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Night...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.62,0:13:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is coming again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.05,0:13:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody... Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let my child die...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Fruit!\N--Everyone, food!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apples!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.52,0:13:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet this is a gift\Nfrom the Flower Capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take some to my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.36,0:13:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had anything in a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's share with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:13:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone left me an apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eat it with gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.46,0:14:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can breast-feed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Kaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those swine ate\Nthe leftover faulty Smiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat! Eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And follow in Ebisu Town's footsteps!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when you're starved or\Nyour family dies, you'll laugh foolishly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only fitting for you maggots!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you wonderful days of smiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't start crying suddenly, you tramp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying! Laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.37,0:15:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Entertain me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excite me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a banquet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat and drink...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad and mom are both dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.63,0:16:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Komurasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was exactly as I wanted it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You started working at the Pleasure Hall\Nof your own will, you slut!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna get your revenge on me\Nthat much?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop playing the victim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still remember my grudge against\Nthe Kozuki Clan and what they did to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you're doing is\Nthe same as what they did to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill everyone who rebels against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna just die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Komurasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:17:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's drink together again\Nin the next life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my samurai retainers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oden's legacy persists!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To bury me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was despised just for living...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fathom my grudge against them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take the Kurozumi Clan's\Nresentment lightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.23,0:17:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want everything to be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You are the moon unaware of the dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May your purpose be fulfilled
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and cast nine shadows on the night\Nwoven of 20 years
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you shall know\Nthe brilliance of the dawn"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foxfire Kin'emon and the Akazaya samurai...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot wait to face them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will cut them down with a single stroke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a dreadful scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:19.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,MAY OROCHI BE GONE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:27.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,GET US OUT OF HELL
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Move Onigashima out of the way"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.97,0:19:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried many times, but I could not do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Momonosuke!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:20:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leap 20 years into the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and rebuild the Kozuki Clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I know you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hard work and dedication\Nwill touch everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiyori!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to hold on now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or I will bring shame to the Kozuki Clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momonosuke-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is believing in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not going to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There! There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kin'emon! Kiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still alive, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.29,0:20:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you ever die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take down Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only Kaido were gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.84,0:21:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only Kaido were gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only Kaido were gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only Kaido were gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw hat man...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our 20-year battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until Kaido is gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until Kaido is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.62,0:21:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will never end!
